   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mental Health Support to 1600 pupils in Gulu,</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will support 1600 Pupil in post conflict Gulu district who suffered  trauma, mental health conditions, epilepsy domestic violence during  20years of LRA war. the project will  offers psycho education, mental health sensitization, home visits, diagnostic assessments, referral, debates on mental health issues that affects pupils, talking compound/anti stigma    This will done through outreaches,  collaboration with school administration, partners in educations and  health department.</narrative>
  </description>
